# OpenAPI Generator Ignore
# Lines beginning with a # are comments
# Patterns follow .gitignore format

# Prevent overwriting custom service implementations
**/service/*ServiceImpl.java
**/service/*ServiceImpl.kt

# Keep hand-written models
**/dto/CustomModel.java
**/dto/CustomModel.kt

# Skip test/doc generation (better to use generateApiTests=false in Gradle)
**/*Test.java
**/*Test.kt
**/*.md

# Preserve custom interceptors
**/interceptor/CustomInterceptor.java
**/interceptor/CustomInterceptor.kt
